WEBVTT

00:05:57.469 --> 00:06:00.143
bottom half carbon in the atmosphere

00:06:00.143 --> 00:06:02.546
where it's driving climate change.

00:06:02.546 --> 00:06:05.034
In fact, the number two cause

00:06:05.034 --> 00:06:07.573
of carbon being released
into the atmosphere

00:06:07.573 --> 00:06:10.411
is forest destruction.

00:06:10.411 --> 00:06:12.227
But in talking about destruction,

00:06:12.227 --> 00:06:14.171
it's important to keep in mind

00:06:14.171 --> 00:06:18.174
that the Amazon is the mightiest
landscape of all.

00:06:18.174 --> 00:06:20.626
It's a place of beauty and wonder.

00:06:20.626 --> 00:06:23.117
The biggest anteater in the world

00:06:23.117 --> 00:06:25.065
lives in the rain forest,

00:06:25.065 --> 00:06:27.468
tips the scale at 90 pounds.

00:06:27.468 --> 00:06:29.519
The goliath bird-eating spider

00:06:29.519 --> 00:06:31.467
is the world's largest spider.